{"tid":2164544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國防部運用Minecraft訓練AI輔助人類","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:05:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc1a02e4ca574557a5daaf82d91af809c0f3959","tid":2164544,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sites.breakingmedia.com/uploads/sites/3/2020/08/6187224-768x530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.breakingmedia.com%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2020%2F08%2F6187224-768x530.jpg&h=c72d7d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《Breaking Defense》網站報導，在美國國防部的構想下，AI在未來將會擔任美軍人員作戰時的輔助角色，例如「忠誠僚機」計畫，讓搭載AI無人機協助真人飛行員執行任務，或是士兵在射擊時，使用AI瞄準系統，提升命中率；除了在前線，AI也可以參與制定攻擊計畫、後勤補給等繁雜的參謀事務，在未來橫跨陸、海、空、網路和太空領域的「聯合全領域作戰」上，AI將扮演非常重要的角色。<br />\n<br />\n但要實現上述概念，AI必須具備可信賴的能力，以及建立和人類官兵有效溝通的模式，才能應付瞬息萬變的戰場。因此美國國防高等研究計劃署（DARPA）與位在麻省的Aptima公司合作，進行「可能任務調適性分配」計畫（ADAPT），探索人機協同作戰的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n《Minecraft》擁有極高的自由度，允許多人一同探索、建造遊戲地圖和場景，打造不同的任務目標，並且《Minecraft》開放原始碼，Aptima公司可以在遊戲中插入客製的智慧型代理（AI agent），在模擬真實世界的關卡中，觀摩人類玩家的行為，進一步分析出人類與AI的合作模式，再發出任務指示。AI如果能理解人類做決策時背後的邏輯，並推算出可能的發展，將成為指揮官在戰場時的「超級副手」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3265022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3265022&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=3b06ea0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3265022&h=8337cbff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3265022</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://breakingdefense.com/2020/08/darpa-trains-ai-to-understand-humans-in-minecraft/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fdarpa-trains-ai-to-understand-humans-in-minecraft%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f9e7147f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://breakingdefense.com/2020/08/darpa-trains-ai-to-understand-humans-in-minecraft/</a>"},{"pid":"f9e7582b793d162e6524007df10d721dda5301d7","tid":2164544,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"我地偉大嘅中國用嘴炮都打贏你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbaa2731d43e6386a365a9c7b0e2e4f94efd98e","tid":2164544,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"Creeper? Oh~~~ man"}]}